---

## Summary

> **The core interview pipeline is functional**: question retrieval → present question (with TTS) → answer via typing or speech (STT) → LLM evaluation → body language analysis. The app works end-to-end as a prototype.
>
> **Key gaps**: no session reports, no progress tracking, no resume parsing, no communication skills analysis, and no documentation.
